<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- حُبِسَ ظُلْمًا، أَوْ بِمَطَرٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- أَوْ أَقَامَ لِحَاجَةٍ بِلَا نِيَّةِ إِقَامَةٍ فَوْقَ أَرْبَعَةِ أَيَّامٍ، وَلَا يَدْرِي مَتَى تَنْقَضِي.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَصَرَ أَبَدًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- يُبَاحُ جَمْعٌ بَيْنَ ظُهْرٍ وَعَصْرٍ وَعِشَاءَيْنِ بِوَقْتِ إِحْدَاهُمَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَتَرْكُهُ أَفْضَلُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> غَيْرَ جَمْعَيْ عَرَفَةَ وَمُزْدَلِفَةَ:</span> فَيُسَنُّ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيُجْمَعُ فِي ثَمَانِ حَالَاتٍ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> بِسَفَرِ قَصْرٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَمَرِيضٍ يَلْحَقُهُ بِتَرْكِهِ مَشَقَّةٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَمُرْضِعٍ لِمَشَقَّةِ كَثْرَةِ نَجَاسَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَمُسْتَحَاضَةٍ وَنَحْوِهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَعَاجِزٍ عَنْ طَهَارَةٍ أَوْ تَيَمُّمٍ لِكُلِّ صَلَاةٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> أَوْ عَنْ مَعْرِفَةِ وَقْتٍ؛ كَأَعْمَى وَنَحْوِهِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٧]</span> <span style="color:#707070">[٨]</span> وَلِعُذْرٍ، أَوْ شُغْلٍ يُبِيحُ تَرْكَ جُمُعَةٍ وَجَمَاعَةٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>